  <div id="mainContent"> 
   <h2>Creating a Safe and Secure Campus</h2> 
   <p> Everyone can play a role in safety, security and emergency preparedness at <abbr class="initialism" title="University of Wisconsin">UW</abbr>–Madison. </p> 
   <p> Learn your part by exploring information on crime prevention, campus resources and emergency procedures. Together, we can enhance the safety and security of everyone who visits, studies or works at the university. </p> 
   <div id="news" class="rounded"> 
